System Requirements

1. PHP version 5.6 or higher
2. PHP Curl extension
3. PHP JSON extension


Installation

1. Copy the files in the web server folder root
2. If you are using a web server other than Apache, configure the web server to forward all requests to the index.php file.


Getting Started

1. To display the contents of the home page river, point your browser to http://localhost/
2. To display the contents for a specific tag, point your browser to http://localhost/[tag]/, e.g. http://localhost/google/


Testing

PHPUnit is already included (via composer) and configured for this sample project and Unit Tests are created for the home page, 'google' and 'facebook' tags

To run the tests execute the following command from the linux shell:

./vendor/phpunit/phpunit/phpunit

